{"tid":1986014,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉載］手足係Kindle出版咗本反送中的書，希望大家支持","createTime":"2020-04-23T14:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T10:08:40.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"42dc47b1c5643b259ca1d2845bca58dad655d0f6","tid":1986014,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:11:01.000Z","msg":"Kindle （即Amazon）Link 請廣傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B087G3LZCH/ref=cm_sw_r_tw_dp_U_x_0HxOEb143718J\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB087G3LZCH%2Fref%3Dcm_sw_r_tw_dp_U_x_0HxOEb143718J&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=f9c500cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/dp/B087G3LZCH/ref=cm_sw_r_tw_dp_U_x_0HxOEb143718J</a><br />\n只有你有手機，都可以下載Kindle App然後試閱，並不限於Kindle機。<br />\n<br />\n港共最近出版咗本<span style=\"color: red;\">《哭泣的城市》，肆意抹黑抗爭運動。</span>最弊係，港共掌握了全港連鎖書店，令到所有出入書店的學生及市民都很可能遭受洗腦。<br />\n我地絕唔可以坐以待斃，<span style=\"color: red;\">不能係書籍呢個文宣領域中敗給敵人</span>。<br />\n其實，去年12月開始，我地手足已經開始撰寫一本書，去分析反送中運動，宣傳抗爭思想。而最近呢個月為了對抗《哭泣的城市》，更加通宵達旦咁趕稿，今天終於成功係kindle上出版。希望大家可以幫忙分享推廣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3wH3ho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3wH3ho.jpg&h=caffc9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：呢本書以文字為主，圖片較少。注重分析及思辨。內容主要係通過反送中運動，去介紹後現代的社會學及哲學理論。直接D講，係有D悶，希望大家多多包涵。<br />\n<br />\n順便，大家都可以關注我地的Youtube Channel「思想加」：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCulMs0FGwozR1mj1a7-BuDw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCulMs0FGwozR1mj1a7-BuDw%2F&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=455265cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCulMs0FGwozR1mj1a7-BuDw/</a><br />\n<br />\n原post<br />\n【突發】手足係Kindle出版咗本反送中的書，希望大家支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1985771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1985771</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b304fad85a6e5545d4a570f10150304021b45c8","tid":1986014,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:46:13.000Z","msg":"［TVB日任23/4］Pampers紙尿片 讓蟲蟲親近BB肌膚？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1985972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1985972</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"012f574c4d0f498c74c7d963334c8caf1deaf2ac","tid":1986014,"uid":5397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T17:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f1a0fd0f0f906f1d7b748852f86fa3bec8594d","tid":1986014,"uid":153151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7b6bc28f60939fed7d5029d66a90736dd25185","tid":1986014,"uid":12662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:30:10.000Z","msg":"見到有呀，但無買。<br />\n睇書想輕鬆吓"},{"pid":"0c1179de6ab5b00b28b7fee06aab1ee8a9f4e516","tid":1986014,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044e674253922a366735d7bbd516f7e1bf77dfbf","tid":1986014,"uid":314604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}